<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo {
            max-width: 150px;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="header">
        <img src="https://d2pznqasld4zpy.cloudfront.net/common/WebLogo.svg" alt="Company Logo" class="logo">
        <h2>Payment Request!</h2>
    </div>

    <p>Dear <%= patient_name %>,</p>

    <div>
        <h2>Clinic Details: </h2>
        <p>Clinic: <%= clinic_details.name %></p>
        <p>Address: <%= clinic_details.address %></p>
        <p>Contact: <%= clinic_details.contact %></p>
        <p>Email: <%= clinic_details.email %></p>
    </div>

    <p>
        We've shared your invoice <%= invoice_code %> dated <%= invoice_date %> for the services provided at <%= clinic_details.name %>.
        The invoice is attached for your reference, and you can make the payment easily using the Pay Now button below.
    </p>
    <% if (payment_status === 'UNPAID' && payment_link) { %>
        <div>
            <a href="<%= payment_link %>">
            Pay Now â‚¬ <%= total_amount %>
            </a>
        </div>
    <% } %>
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, feel free to reach out to us or contact the hospital directly.</p>
    <div class="footer">
        <p>Warm regards,<br>The Sendscript Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
